eanings":["Some characteristic forenames:  Italian Vito, Angelo, Antonio, Salvatore, Giuseppe, Santo, Giovanna, Nicola, Aldo, Baldassare, Carmelo, Carmino.","Italian: from the personal name <i>Adamo</i>, the Italian form of   Adam  ."]},{"name":"Addams","meanings":["English: variant of   Adams  ."]}]},{"name":"Mary","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["From Latin <i>Maria</i> via Old Welsh <i>Meir</i>.  See  <b>Mary</b> ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mary Adams was born in 1596, in England, United Kingdom. She had at least 2 sons and 3 daughters with Jacob Adams."},"et":{"1596–":"1596–Surnud","1575–1633":"1575–1633","1603–1637":"1603–1637","–1670":"–1670","–Male":"Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1596–Female":"1596–Surnud","1633":"1633","1575":"1575","1596":"1596","July 1603":"juuli 1603","1670":"1670","1637":"1637","1603":"1603","London, Greater London, England":"Blendon, London, Inglismaa, United Kingdom",", , England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1596–":"1596–Kuollut","1575–1633":"1575–1633","1603–1637":"1603–1637","–1670":"–1670","–Male":"Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1596–Female":"1596–Kuollut","1633":"1633","1575":"1575","1596":"1596","July 1603":"heinäkuu 1603","1670":"1670","1637":"1637","1603":"1603","London, Greater London, England":"Blendon, London, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta",", , England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1596–":"1596–Décédée","1575–1633":"1575–1633","1603–1637":"1603–1637","–1670":"–1670","–Male":"Décédé","–Female":"Décédée","1596–Female":"1596–Décédée","1633":"1633","1575":"1575","1596":"1596","July 1603":"juillet 1603","1670":"1670","1637":"1637","1603":"1603","London, Greater London, England":"Blendon, Londres, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni",", , England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mary Adams est née en 1596, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 2 fils et 3 filles avec Jacob Adams."},"de":{"1596–":"1596–Vers